data.description: This great 3 bed 2.5 bath home has it all. An awesome main channel lake view from the large, covered deck with a large fenced-in area for your pets. Fill the included golf cart with everything you need for a day on the lake and drive on the blacktop road to the private dock that includes a 10’x24’ boat slip w/lift and a swim platform. Beyond the exceptional lake amenities, a 4-car garage awaits – a haven not just for vehicles, but for your passions. Revel in the shop area that invites you to create, tinker, and explore your interests. With ample space to park your vehicles and accommodate your pursuits, this garage is a haven that transcends practicality. Minutes away from the Boat House Bar & Grill by boat or car, and very close to the Bagnell Dam strip and all the shopping conveniences the area has to offer.
